`8Keywords``   : Purchase_Key
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

The purchase key command gives you the option of purchasing another key for
your room at 1000 gold a piece. We encourage you to buy only  a few keys if
any, because this compromises the security of your  personal room.

